{{Quote|You'll take a ship to raid the fishing villages of the Stony Shore.|Balon to Theon Greyjoy|What is Dead May Never Die}}
The '''Stony Shore''' is a region in [[the North]]. It forms part of the west coast, west of [[the Rills]] and southwest of the [[Wolfswood]] and [[Sea Dragon Point]].&lt;ref&gt;[http://viewers-guide.hbo.com/game-of-thrones/season2/#!/locations/torrhens-square/ HBO viewers guide, season 2 map, Torrhen's Square entry]&lt;/ref&gt;
